.fb-landing__commitment-container.py-3.py-md-5
  .container
    .row.justify-content-md-center
      .col-md-7
        h2.fb-landing__heading-h2.mt-5.mb-4.mb-md-5.text-center
          span.d-block.font-black
            ' Our Commitment to Student Teams

    .row.justify-content-md-center
      .col-md-4.d-flex.align-items-start.fb-landing__commitment-content.p-4
        = image_tag 'fb/students-team-selection-icon.svg', class: 'fb-landing__commitment-icon img-fluid', alt: 'Fairness in Selection'
        .ml-3
          h4.font-semibold
            | Fairness in Selection
          p.fb-landing__commitment-p
            ' Individual students or teams of 2-4 students who are currently pursuing their undergrad
            ' can apply and they would be selected through different
            | campaign methods.

      .col-md-4.d-flex.align-items-start.fb-landing__commitment-content.p-4
        = image_tag 'fb/students-skills-icon.svg', class: 'fb-landing__commitment-icon img-fluid', alt: 'Knowledge, Skill and Learning'
        .ml-3
          h4.font-semibold
            | Knowledge, Skill and Learning
          p.fb-landing__commitment-p
            ' Students would be on-boarded the SV.CO Online Learning Platform and
            | supported with Human Assisted Learning on a Action Learning (Learn by Doing) pedagogy.

      .w-100

      .col-md-4.d-flex.align-items-start.fb-landing__commitment-content.p-4
        = image_tag 'fb/students-guidance-icon.svg', class: 'fb-landing__commitment-icon img-fluid', alt: 'Guidance and Assessment'
        .ml-3
          h4.font-semibold
            | Guidance and Assessment
          p.fb-landing__commitment-p
            ' The select teams will be announced by Facebook India and will get an
            | opportunity to present their product demo results to the leadership panel identified.

      .col-md-4.d-flex.align-items-start.fb-landing__commitment-content.p-4
        = image_tag 'fb/students-future-icon.svg', class: 'fb-landing__commitment-icon img-fluid', alt: 'Future Prospects'
        .ml-3
          h4.font-semibold
            | Future Prospects
          p.fb-landing__commitment-p
            ' Based on whether they have customer success, they can choose to build
            | a startup or use their skills to get great jobs in other startups.

.fb-landing__stakeholders-container.py-3.py-md-5
  .container
    .row.justify-content-md-center
      .col-md-7
        h2.fb-landing__heading-h2.mt-5.mb-4.text-center
          span.d-block.font-black
            ' Stakeholders

        p.fb-landing__content-p.text-center.mb-4
